

what .js lang can do on HTML-page ?

js-lang can bring any dynamic-behav to html page thru web-APIs

web-APIs are implememnted and abstracted as js objects/functions by browsers.

e,g  web-APIs  ( DOM , XHR , Timer , etc... ) 

using DOM API
--------------
  --> can create/update/delete/delect html elements.
  --> can change element's attributes
  --> can change element's style
  --> can change element's inner-html
  --> can handle events on elements
  --> can create rich UI components.
  --> can validate form-fields

ising XHR API
---------------
  --> can communicate with server async and update result to page. ( AJAX )


HTML5 APIs
--------------

 a. canvas
 b. audio/video
 c. localStorage
 d. geo
 c. webworker
 d. SSE
 g. wesockets
 e. WebGL

 etc..........


----------------------------------------


complexities of plain-js ( script written by you with web-apis )


  1.  browser compatibility.
  2.  too much code even for simple oprns.
  3.  performance issues  ( e.g DOM related operns )
  4.  memory manangement
  5.  data-binding is manual


solns 

  using JS-libraries and Frameworks

  1. jQuery

  Limitations wlith jQuery

  --> close to DOM. ( View )
  --> data-binding manual.
  --> view+logic+data atr mixed

